#: en/gimp-using-variable-size-brush.html:57(p)
msgid "You can get the brush size varying in three ways:"
msgstr ""

#: en/gimp-using-variable-size-brush.html:63(p)
msgid "Using the <span class=\"guilabel\">Scale</span> slider of the tool that uses the brush. Pencil, Paintbrush, Eraser, Airbrush, Clone, Heal, Perspective Clone, Blur/Sharpen and Dodge/Burn tools have a slider to vary brush size."
